    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Burmese Buddhist ribbons or tapes traditionally used to bind palm leaf manuscripts. Produced as a devotional act of merit making, they can contain Buddhist texts and illustrations woven into the textile.</Note_Text>
